title: UCLA vs. Cal football: Score, live updates and game chat
text:
We have a potential upset brewing in California.
The No. 20 California Golden Bears are trailing the UCLA Bruins 26-10 in the second half of a Week 8 Pac-12 football rivalry game on Thursday night. (TV on ESPN, Comcast/Xfinity channel 35 or 735 for HD)
More : Pac-12, College football scores for Week 8
Catch the latest live updates and analysis, photos and video highlights from the game in the comments section below. Have thoughts on how Cal or UCLA are performing against their bitter rivals? Don't hesitate to jump in on the live updates and chat with us as the game rolls along.
